      "writtenOn": "2026-04-15T10:35:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Implemented connection preservation in setProxyDevicesData \nmutation. When data reloads, active connections are maintained:\n\nif (currentDevice?.isActive \u0026\u0026 currentDevice?.file) {\n  return {\n    ...newDevice,\n    file: currentDevice.file,      // Preserved\n    nbd: currentDevice.nbd,        // Preserved\n    isActive: currentDevice.isActive,\n  };\n}\n\nThis prevents WebSocket connection loss during SPA navigation, exactly \nas you outlined.",
